				          <div class="itemhead">
                          
                           		            <h1><a href="http://blogs.babble.com/family-kitchen/2011/06/22/10-summertime-watermelon-recipes/" rel="bookmark">10 Summertime Watermelon Recipes</a></h1>

				            <div class="author">Posted by <a href="/family-kitchen/?author=85">laurasrecipes </a> on June 22nd, 2011 at 11:33 am  </div><span class="printbutton">
<a href="#" onclick="window.print()"><img src="http://cdn.babble.com/family-kitchen/wp-content/themes/family-kitchen/images/print_button_white.jpg" /></a>
</span>
	    			         				
    			    <p><a href="http://cdn.babble.com/family-kitchen/files/2011/06/watermelonpops4sm.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-45525" title="watermelonpops4sm" src="http://cdn.babble.com/family-kitchen/files/2011/06/watermelonpops4sm.jpg" alt="watermelonpops4sm 10 Summertime Watermelon Recipes" width="525" height="349" /></a></p>
<p>Nothing beats the cool refreshing taste of watermelon on a warm summer day. This year get creative and turn that delicious fruit into frosty drinks, ice cold pops or a variety of other unique summer preparations. We rounded up our favorites both from our archives and from some of our favorite blogs. If you have a favorite way to prepare watermelon, we&#8217;d love your suggestions in the comments section.</p>
<p><span id="more-45313"></span><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong>10 Summertime Watermelon Recipes</strong></p>


